Looking for something to do?  Write a [[en/Development/Main Page|patch]] for one of these features!

Requested features that have already been rejected by the OpenTTD developers are marked as '''Rejected'''. Please do ''not'' request those features here or in the forums again. The reasons why a feature was rejected and further information can be found under [[en/Archive/Community/Rejected features]].

